    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A white or other colored crêpe made of artificial or raw silk fiber in plain weave with normal chain and weft of alternately two right and two left twisted yarns.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
